---
/* Process.astro — Updated messaging for Audit → Fix → Scale */
---

<section class="bg-slate-950 text-white py-20 lg:py-24 border-t border-slate-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-16 text-center lg:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold mb-4">
        How we approach growth
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        We don’t start by building or running ads.
        We start by understanding whether your website is ready to scale safely.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Phase 1
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">
  Customer Leak Scan Call
</h3>

<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
  In a 20–30 minute call, we review your website live and identify
  where potential customers are dropping off.
</p>

      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Phase 2
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">
          Fix the system
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          If risks are found, we rebuild or optimize your website into a
          high-performance, fully owned growth asset.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Phase 3
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">
          Scale with confidence
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Once the system is solid, you can run ads, SEO, and campaigns knowing
          every dollar is landing on a reliable foundation.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Closing note -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-4 border-t border-slate-800 max-w-xl">
      <a
        href="/process"
        class="text-slate-400 hover:underline hover:text-white transition text-md"
      >
        See the full process →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
